# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者做生意嘅時候，為咗唔令損失越來越大，盡快賣出或者停止投資，減少損失嘅行為。（量詞：吓）
eng:to cut losses
<eg>
yue:見個股價一路跌，我決定止蝕，唔好再等喇。 (gin3 go3 guk6 ga3 jat6 lou6 dit3, ngo5 git3 ding6 ji2 sik1, m4 hou2 zai3 dang2 laa1.)
eng:Seeing the stock price kept falling, I decided to cut my losses and not wait any longer.

<eg>
yue:佢喺賭波輸咗好多錢，諗住再博一鋪止蝕，點知仲輸多咗。 (keoi5 hai2 dou2 bo1 syu1 zo2 hou2 do1 cin4, nam2 zung6 zoi3 bok3 jat1 pou1 ji2 sik1, dim2 zi1 zung6 syu1 do1 zo2.)
eng:He lost a lot of money gambling, and thought he could recoup his losses with one more bet, but ended up losing even more.
 [end of text]


